videos.description: Quade Green dishes it out to Hamidou Diallo who drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Diallo sinks 3 for Kentucky

videos.description: Kentucky's defense can't handle Collin Sexton, who drills a jumper with two defenders on him.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton drains heavily contested jumper

videos.description: PJ Washington shows no mercy and pulverizes the rim with an emphatic slam.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Washington punishes the rim

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander lobs it up to Sacha Killeya-Jones for a two-hand jam to pump up the crowd.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Killeya-Jones gets feed for dunk

videos.description: Dazon Ingram drives to the rim for a layup but is met by an emphatic block by Wenyen Gabriel.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Gabriel denies Ingram at rim

videos.description: Collin Sexton drives to the basket and switches hands mid-air for a layup and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Sexton gets acrobatic layup to fall

videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel gets Wildcats and their fans rockin' after drilling a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Gabriel fired up after draining trey
